{"type": "article", "id": 13988, "title": "实心自行车轮胎", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-26T07:49:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101212NVHA63MvL1ZYXxow.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自韩国的自行车公司 Tannus TIRE 十几年来一直专注生产非充气的实心自行车轮胎，今年他们推出了 Aither1.1 新版本，他们使用一种叫做“微闭孔微发泡聚合树脂”的特殊材料，可以在防扎破，侵蚀和老化的同时，保证较为轻的质量和时尚的外观，抛弃补胎工具，为骑行复杂的路段提供了便利。目前公司提供了三种硬度的轮胎，同时有黑色，黄色，红色，白色等 12 种颜色可以选择，售价 140 美元，<a href=\"http://www.tannus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416256mRUJSq2vErIO71w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75477707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141625x2SWRIagEULjqw8D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141625wI6TneAt1SkWFjxZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74806202\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416268UTfNB7DMyPwoxa3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141626Q6hK3uw92TOEbgPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416276eCoEsDlbZyxzdk7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}